      "acceptanceCriteria": "The validated QoI (hemolysis index) must be directly mapped to the clinical decision threshold with documented traceability at Gradation 3.",
      "rationale": "The modified index of hemolysis (MIH) used in simulation differs from the normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) used in the clinical threshold specification. Traceability between these metrics is partially documented. Achieved level 2."
    },
