      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity analysis and uncertainty quantification on all model input parameters (viscosity, density, hemolysis model coefficients) must be completed at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated for geometric tolerances but was not completed for hemolysis model coefficients (C and alpha in the power-law model), which carry the largest sensitivity. Partial UQ coverage yields achieved level 2. Epistemic gap."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
