      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of sample-to-sample variability in experimental hemolysis measurements must be provided with sufficient replicates at Gradation 3.",
      "rationale": "Only single experimental runs were available for each operating condition. No replicate measurements were conducted and inter-sample variability in the blood analog preparation was not characterized. Epistemic gap."
