    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 at MRL 5 has been reviewed. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated: 7 factors were formally assessed and all achieved levels below required levels; 6 factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. Despite the gap profile, the package is accepted for submission as a complete MRL 5 credibility dossier documenting the current state of evidence. The decision record reflects acceptance of the assessment package itself, not acceptance of the model for regulatory use. Residual gaps must be resolved prior to device submission.",
